high_descs: Turn left, go forward, turn right at the drying rack of the sink.
Take the large knife from the rack.
Cut the potato on the rack into slices.
Go right a step and face towards the sink.
Put the knife in the sink basin.
Go left a step and face towards the drying rack.
Take a slice of potato from the rack.
Turn right, go forward, turn left and go forward to the stand with the microwave.
Cook the potato in the microwave. Take the potato out of the microwave.
Turn left, go to the wall, turn left, go straight to the counter with the black plate.
Put the potato in the green bin under the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked slice of potato in a bin.

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the potato on the sink.
Pick up the yellow knife to the right of the kettle.
Cut up the potato closest to the window.
Walk to the sink on the right.
Place the knife into the sink.
Walk to the cut up potato on the sink.
Pick up a piece of the potato.
Turn around and walk to the microwave to the right of the fridge.
Microwave the piece of potato and then pick the piece of potato up from the microwave.
Turn around and walk to the green recycling bin.
Place the piece of potato in the green recycling bin.
anns.task_desc: Place a microwaved piece of potato into the green recycling bin.

high_descs: turn left and walk over to the kitchen sink on the right
grab the knife off of the kitchen sink cover
slice up the potato on top of the kitchen sink cover on the back side
move to the right a bit and face the kitchen sink again
place the knife inside of the right side kitchen sink
move to the left and face the left side of the kitchen sink
grab a slice of potato off of the kitchen sink
turn right and walk over to the microwave on the right side of the room
place the potato slice inside of the microwave, cook it, then take it back out
turn left and walk to the end of the room, then turn left and walk to the end of the room
place the potato slice inside of the garbage bin below
anns.task_desc: place a microwaved potato slice inside of the garbage bin

high_descs: Turn left then face the sink on your right.
Take the knife from the sink in front of you.
Slice the potato on the sink in front of you.
Turn right, then face the sink on your left.
Place the knife in the sink in front of you.
Turn left, then right and face the sink in front of you.
Take a potato slice from the sink in front of you.
Turn right, then right again and head towards the microwave in front of you.
Heat up the potato slice in the microwave in front of you, take it out and close it.
Turn around and head towards the green recycling bin in front of you.
Place the potato slice in the recycling bin.
anns.task_desc: Put a hot potato slice in the recycling bin.

high_descs: Go to the left, walk straight and stop in front of the counter top next to the sink.
Pick up the knife from on top of the sink.
Cut the potato near the faucet into slices using the knife.
Walk slightly to the left to get to the sink.
Put the knife in the sink.
Walk back to the counter top next to the sink again.
Pick up a slice of the potato that you just cut.
Walk to the right and turn right to go to the black cabinet with a microwave on top of it.
Open the microwave, cook it for a few seconds, open the microwave to pick up the potato and close the microwave.
Walk to the left, turn to the left at the end of the room and walk to the recycling bin.
Throw the cooked slice of potato in the recycling bin
anns.task_desc: Throw away a cooked slice of potato in the recycling bin which is across the fridge.
